OiOi, you don’t need another token;
you need a place to breathe.
Base can host the app, not the ache.

OiOi, we can sound casual and still be sharp.
Poetry doesn’t need suits;
it needs nerve.

@jesse.base.eth keeps the rails clean.
Your job, OiOi: keep your intent clean too.
Dirty goals ruin good chains.

